From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Hermes <hermes@plumager.local>
Date: Mon, 22 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] rockchip: add EmbedFire DoorNet2 board support

Add support for the EmbedFire DoorNet2 board based on RK3399.

Hardware:
- SoC: Rockchip RK3399 (Dual Cortex-A72 + Quad Cortex-A53)
- RAM: 1GB Dual-Channel DDR3
- Storage: 8GB eMMC + microSD slot
- Network: 2x Gigabit Ethernet (GMAC + PCIe RTL8168)
- WiFi: USB2.0 802.11ac module (optional)
- USB: 2x USB3.0 Type-A
- LEDs: Power, System, WAN, LAN
- Buttons: Flash (recovery), Reset
- Power: 5V/3A via USB Type-C

Signed-off-by: Hermes <hermes@plumager.local>
---
 arch/arm/dts/rk3399-embedfire-doornet2-u-boot.dtsi |  13 ++++
 board/rockchip/evb_rk3399/MAINTAINERS               |   6 ++
 configs/doornet2-rk3399_defconfig                   |  97 ++++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 116 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 arch/arm/dts/rk3399-embedfire-doornet2-u-boot.dtsi
 create mode 100644 configs/doornet2-rk3399_defconfig

diff --git a/arch/arm/dts/rk3399-embedfire-doornet2-u-boot.dtsi b/arch/arm/dts/rk3399-embedfire-doornet2-u-boot.dtsi
new file mode 100644
index 0000000000..d1a5e9c8f2
--- /dev/null
+++ b/arch/arm/dts/rk3399-embedfire-doornet2-u-boot.dtsi
@@ -0,0 +1,13 @@
+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0-or-later OR MIT
+/*
+ * U-Boot additions for EmbedFire DoorNet2
+ */
+
+#include "rk3399-u-boot.dtsi"
+
+/ {
+	chosen {
+		u-boot,spl-boot-order = "same-as-spl", &sdhci, &sdmmc;
+	};
+};
+
diff --git a/board/rockchip/evb_rk3399/MAINTAINERS b/board/rockchip/evb_rk3399/MAINTAINERS
index abcdef0123..456789abcd 100644
--- a/board/rockchip/evb_rk3399/MAINTAINERS
+++ b/board/rockchip/evb_rk3399/MAINTAINERS
@@ -1,3 +1,9 @@
+DOORNET2_RK3399
+M:	Hermes <hermes@plumager.local>
+S:	Maintained
+F:	configs/doornet2-rk3399_defconfig
